EN: This construction foreman is highly respected on the construction site.
ZH: 包工头负责监督工人的工作进度。
EN: The construction foreman is responsible for overseeing the progress of the workers.
ZH: 这位包工头经验丰富，工作很细致。
EN: This experienced construction foreman is meticulous in his work.
