EN: The construction foreman is responsible for ensuring the safety of the construction site.
ZH: 这个包工头每天都早早来到工地。
EN: This construction foreman arrives at the construction site early every day.
ZH: 包工头需要对施工过程进行全面的掌控。
EN: Construction foremen need to have full control over the construction process.
