EN: This construction foreman is very strict and demands that workers adhere to technical standards.
ZH: 包工头需要与其他承包商协商合作事宜。
EN: Construction foremen need to negotiate and collaborate with other contractors.
ZH: 这个包工头能够高效地组织队伍完成任务。
EN: This construction foreman is able to efficiently organize the team to complete tasks.
ZH: 包工头的责任是确保工地材料的供应充足。
EN: The responsibility of the construction foreman is to ensure an adequate supply of materials at the construction site.
